      <title>亚洲兴业银行交易员在期权押注未被发现后退出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/socgen-traders-in-asia-exited-after-options-bets-went-undetected</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，法国兴业银行发现了一批风险押注，但该公司的风险管理系统没有发现，导致这家法国银行的两名交易员离开了该公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/socgen-traders-in-asia-exited-after-options-bets-went-undetected</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 00:00:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
